    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold as a reliable, though aesthetically aged, daily driver. The exterior shows its age with noticeable fading in the clear coat, several door dings, and some minor rust spots on the lower panels. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, and some of the interior trim pieces have become loose over time. While the engine and transmission are functional, the car would benefit from a suspension refresh and a thorough detailing to bring it back to a better state. This is an ideal choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly option who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance needs.",
