      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready to work for you? This vehicle is in honest, fair condition and represents a fantastic opportunity for someone who values reliable transportation at a great price! While it shows some expected wear and tear from its time on the road, it remains a solid, functional choice for your commuting needs. It's a practical, straightforward car that\u2019s eager to start its next chapter with a new owner!",
