      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly flawless condition inside and out\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and meticulously cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
