    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E92 M3, featuring the legendary naturally aspirated 4.0L S65 V8 engine and a lightning-quick M-DCT dual-clutch transmission. This example is in museum-quality condition, with original factory paint and an interior showing zero bolster wear or trim degradation. Mechanically, it is fully sorted with documented preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The M Variable Differential Lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) function flawlessly, ensuring peak chassis dynamics. A truly pristine specimen with a comprehensive service history, preserved in its original mechanical configuration.",
