      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece for the discerning collector: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior retains its original factory scent and supple, uncreased leather. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive binder of documentation included. From the flawless alloy wheels to the untouched engine bay, every inch of this vehicle reflects a standard of care rarely seen. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule offering a showroom-fresh experience. No accidents, no modifications, and absolutely no compromises.",
